<HEADLINE> Fujian Industry Shows Sound Performance in First Half </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The industries at township level
and above in east China's Fujian Province contributed a combined
output value of nearly 97 billion yuan in the first half of this
year, up 17.8 percent over the same period of last year.
