<HEADLINE> Bulgarian Coach Signs With Saudi Arabia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Saudi Arabian club Al-Nassr has
signed a one-year contract with Bulgaria's Dimitar Penev, who was
the head coach of Bulgaria's team in 1994.
</P>
<P>
