<HEADLINE> Singapore PM Regrets Over Cambodia's Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Singapore Prime Minister Goh
Chok Tong expressed his regret over the recent crisis in Cambodia
when meeting Cambodian First Prime Minister Prince Norodom
Ranariddh here today.
</P>
<P>
Ranariddh, who arrived here on Sunday, called on Goh to discuss
recent developments in Cambodia, Goh's office said.
