<HEADLINE> PICC Looks to Expand Insurance Business </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The People's Insurance Co (Group)
of China is seeking to expand its business in the coming months to
maintain its lead in the domestic market, today's China Daily
reported.
</P>
<P>
Although the group controls more than 70 percent of the market,
its president Ma Yongwei said "we still want more."
</P>
<P>
